        visited = set()
        stack = deque([(kids_arr[0], 0)])
        while stack:
            node, node_depth = stack.pop()
            if node not in visited:
                visited.add(node)
                if node == kids_arr[-1]:
                    break
                for child in graph[node]:
                    stack.append((child, node_depth + 1))

                depth = min(depth, graph[node][0])
                for child in graph[node]:
                    stack.append(child)
